Mcaster1DNAS TODO List
================================================================================

COMPLETED (v2.5.0):
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
✅ YAML configuration file support
✅ YP connection logging feature
✅ Tabbed admin logs interface
✅ XML/YAML format auto-detection
✅ Comprehensive YAML templates
✅ YP per-server logging

PLANNED FOR v2.6.0:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Configuration:
☐ JSON configuration support
☐ Config validation tool (mcaster1-validate-config)
☐ Config converter tools:
  ☐ mcaster1-xml2yaml
  ☐ mcaster1-yaml2xml
  ☐ mcaster1-json2yaml
☐ Environment variable substitution in configs
☐ Include directives for modular configurations
☐ Config reload without restart (SIGHUP handler improvement)

YP Features:
☐ Log rotation support for YP logs
☐ YP log level configuration (INFO, DEBUG, ERROR filtering)
☐ Real-time YP log viewer in admin interface (without iframe)
☐ YP statistics dashboard showing success/failure rates
☐ Email alerts for YP listing failures
☐ Retry logic improvements for YP failures
☐ Multi-region YP server support with automatic failover

Admin Interface:
☐ Real-time charts and graphs for statistics
☐ WebSocket support for live updates (remove page refresh)
☐ Listener geolocation map
☐ Stream quality metrics dashboard
☐ Mobile-responsive admin interface improvements
☐ Dark mode support
☐ Export logs as CSV/JSON
☐ Advanced filtering for logs viewer
☐ Mount point health monitoring dashboard

Logging:
☐ Structured logging (JSON format option)
☐ Log aggregation support (syslog, rsyslog)
☐ Per-mount access logs with custom formats
☐ Request tracing with correlation IDs
☐ Performance metrics logging

Authentication:
☐ OAuth2 authentication support
☐ LDAP authentication integration
☐ JWT token authentication for API access
☐ Two-factor authentication for admin
☐ API key management

Streaming:
☐ HTTP/2 support
☐ QUIC protocol support
☐ Adaptive bitrate streaming (HLS, DASH)
☐ WebRTC support for ultra-low latency
☐ Opus codec optimizations
☐ AAC-HE v2 support
☐ Multi-codec transcoding

Monitoring:
☐ Prometheus metrics exporter
☐ StatsD integration
☐ Health check endpoints (/health, /ready, /live)
☐ Performance profiling tools
☐ Connection pool monitoring
☐ Buffer usage metrics

Security:
☐ Rate limiting per IP/mount
☐ DDoS protection improvements
☐ Automatic TLS certificate renewal (Let's Encrypt)
☐ Security headers enforcement (CSP, HSTS, etc.)
☐ Audit logging for admin actions
☐ IP whitelist/blacklist improvements

API:
☐ RESTful API for server control
☐ GraphQL API for statistics
☐ WebSocket API for real-time events
☐ API documentation (OpenAPI/Swagger)
☐ API versioning support

Performance:
☐ Zero-copy networking optimizations
☐ Connection pooling for relays
☐ Memory pool allocator
☐ Thread pool sizing improvements
☐ Cache-aware data structures

Documentation:
☐ Interactive web-based documentation
☐ Video tutorials for common tasks
☐ Migration guide from Icecast 2.x
☐ Best practices guide
☐ Troubleshooting flowcharts
☐ Performance tuning guide

Quality of Life:
